---
layout: layouts/base.njk

title: Home

menukey: home
permalink: /index.html
---
<div class='section section--homepage'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col col-xs-12'>
      <div class='row section__floating--horizontal'>
        <div class='col col-xs-12 col-md-7'>
          <div class='section--intro__picture'>
            {% include 'partials/profile-picture.njk' %}
            <img src='/img/memoji.png' alt='Memoji' class='hover-image' />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='col col-xs-12 col-md-5 first-xs last-md'>
          <div class='section--intro__wrapper'>
            <div class='section__header'>
              <h2>Hey.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class='section--intro section__floating section__floating--right-to-left section__floating--center-top'>
              <p>I'm Benjamin, a lead javascript / frontend engineer at Hiber, based in Amsterdam.</p>
              <p>Mostly working with vue.js, but also pushing the boundaries with the latest spec of ES and TypeScript, and a bit of a S/CSS geek.</p>
              <p>When I'm not behind a screen I love to cook food for others, cycle, mix live & studio sound, listen to almost any genre of music (and make noise), contribute to open source, hike in the mountains, and enjoy discovering new cafes.</p>
              {% include 'partials/social.njk' %}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='section section--homepage'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col col-xs-12'>
      <div class='section__header'>
        <h5>Latest GitHub repos</h5>
        <h2>Projects.</h2>
        <a class='section__header__see link--wiggle' href='https://github.com/nothingrandom'>See all <i class='fal fa-eye'></i></a>
      </div>
      <div class='row'>
        {% for repo in github.myRecentRepos %}
          <div class='col-xs-12 col-sm-4 section__item'>
            <a href='{{ repo.html_url }}' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>
              <span class='pip section__item__tag project__language project__language--{% lowercase repo.language %}'>{{ repo.language }}</span>
              <h3 class='section__item__header'>{{ repo.name }}</h3>
              <p class='section__item__description'>{{ repo.description }}</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='section section--homepage--food'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col col-xs-12'>
      <div class='section__header'>
        <h2>Food.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class='row section__item--food'>
        <div class='col-xs-12 col-md-4'>
          <div class='section__intro'>
            <p>It's no secret, I love food. When I'm finished from a day writing code, squishing bugs, and poject mangement there's few things more enjoyable than preparing dinner.</p>
            <p>I publish my recipes here, on this site, mostly as a record for me that doesn't get covered in tomatoes and oil and also for those who want to try some of my favourites.</p>
            <p><a href='/food/'>View recipes.</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='section section--homepage'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col col-xs-12'>
      <div class='section__header'>
        <h5>Recent thoughts</h5>
        <h2>Blog.</h2>
        <a class='section__header__see link--wiggle' href='/blog/'>See all <i class='fal fa-eye'></i></a>
      </div>
      <div class='row'>
        {% for post in collections.posts | limitTo(3) %}
          <div class='col-xs-12 col-sm-4 section__item'>
            {% include 'partials/blog-small-item.njk' %}
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
